name: CRYPTO MOTH - LEPIDOPTERA RARUS 02- APRIL.2021
description:
Burned and reminted editions on my new wallet.
This is the only cryptomoth that is available as a multi-edition and on the Tezos network.
Find the other crypto moths on: https://opensea.io/collection/lottez-animated-crypto-moths

A stunning high resolution piece of animated digital art. Press pause on any given frame to display any of the thousands of unique stills. A combination of hand drawn work combined with digitally reworked glitch art. This particular piece is part of a series of 5 crypto moths released in 2021. Every piece is signed by the artist.  For more info on artist LotteZ visit: www.lottez.com Twitter: @LotteZ13
